      • TymeacIndividualQueue

        public TymeacIndividualQueue(java.lang.String u_name,
                     java.lang.String u_pa_name,
                     java.lang.String u_que_type,
                     java.lang.String u_start_threads,
                     int u_pa_timeout,
                     int u_nbr_threads,
                     int u_nbr_waitlists,
                     int u_nbr_entries,
                     int u_nbr_entries_thresholds,
                     int u_wait_time,
                     int u_kill_time,
                     float u_overall,
                     float u_individual,
                     float u_factor,
                     float u_average)
        Constructor for the Tymeac Individual User Queue
        Parameters:
        u_name - String is the name of the Queue
        u_pa_name - String is the name of the Processing Application Class
        u_que_type - String is the Type of Queue, normal or OA
        u_nbr_threads - int is the number of threads
        u_pa_timeout - int is the PAC timeout value in seconds
        u_nbr_waitlists - int is the number of wait lists
        u_nbr_entries - int is the number of wait list entries
        u_nbr_entries_thresholds - int is the number of wait list entries for thresholds
        u_wait_time - int is the Queue time out value
        u_overall - float is the New Thread Threshold overall percent
        u_individual - float is the New Thread Threshold individual percent
        u_factor - float is the New Thread Threshold weighted factor
